com.ephesoft.dcma.docassembler.classification.engine.process

Class LucenePageProcess

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.dcma.docassembler.classification.engine.process.LucenePageProcess

  • public class LucenePageProcess
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will process every page present at document type Unknown. This will read all the pages one by one and basis of the lucene classification and will create new documents and delete the current page from the document type Unknown.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ephesoft
    See Also:
    DocumentAssembler
